        "## 14.9 Density, mass, and average value over general regions\n",
        "\n",
        "If a thin plate occupies a region $D$ and has density $\\rho(x,y)$, then the mass is\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "m=\\iint_D \\rho(x,y)\\,dA.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "The average value of a function $f$ over $D$ is\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "f_{\\operatorname{avg}}\n",
        "=\n",
        "\\frac{1}{\\operatorname{Area}(D)}\\iint_D f(x,y)\\,dA.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "These formulas are the same as for rectangles, but now the geometry of $D$ must be handled carefully.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Example 14.6: Average value on a triangle\n",
        "\n",
        "Find the average value of\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "f(x,y)=x+2y\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "over\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "D=\\{(x,y):0\\le x\\le 1,\\ 0\\le y\\le 1-x\\}.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "The area is\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\operatorname{Area}(D)=\\frac{1}{2}.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Compute the integral:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{aligned}\n",
        "\\iint_D (x+2y)\\,dA\n",
        "&=\n",
        "\\int_0^1\\int_0^{1-x}(x+2y)\\,dy\\,dx \\\\\n",
        "&=\n",
        "\\int_0^1\\left[xy+y^2\\right]_0^{1-x}\\,dx \\\\\n",
        "&=\n",
        "\\int_0^1\\left(x(1-x)+(1-x)^2\\right)\\,dx \\\\\n",
        "&=\n",
        "\\int_0^1(1-x)\\,dx\n",
        "=\n",
        "\\frac{1}{2}.\n",
        "\\end{aligned}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Thus\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "f_{\\operatorname{avg}}\n",
        "=\n",
        "\\frac{1/2}{1/2}=1.\n",
        "$$"
      ],
      "id": "1c0a93f9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
